title: Game Over
description:
The stories are:

01. News
02. Mai-chan's Secret (This is the prototype for what eventually became "Mai-chan's Daily Life")
03. Mai-chan's Daily Life (The story of a 17 year old maid/slave who is immortal and has impressive regenerative properties)
04. Hao Chi Feng Jiao (The name is Chinese, and it means something like "Good Eats! Feng Jiao.)
05. Song Of The Dull Knife
06. Dining Table Banquet
07. Game Over
08. The Lawless Area Of Oz (A retelling of the classic story)
09. Jingle Bells
10. Guts Marin
